name: What happens in mountains, stays in mountains

metadata.name: What happens in mountains #1
metadata.description:
Photo by Daniil Nemirovsky, artist from Mariupol.

Model: Kateryna Aliinyk, artist from Luhansk.

Photo made on 6h of January 2023, on the Christmas Eve in Orthodox tradition.

Place: Khata-Maysternya, Babyn (near Kosiv), Ivano-Frankivsk region, Ukraine
